# Shopify AI OS — Cursor Rules

## Load first

Read `.ai/AGENTS.md` before any task. Every rule there is binding —
architecture, TypeScript patterns, Shopify constraints, and the 6-step task
loop (locate → plan → skill-gate → implement → validate → report).

## Context loading — pull in only what the task needs

| Need | Load |
|---|---|
| Layer rules, import constraints | `.ai/ARCHITECTURE.md` |
| Shopify integration model, auth | `.ai/PROJECT.md` |
| TypeScript patterns (Result, GIDs, Zod) | `.ai/TYPESCRIPT.md` |
| Term definitions | `.ai/GLOSSARY.md` |
| Shopify surface routing | `.shopify/skills/registry.json` |
| Shopify rules for a surface | `.shopify/skills/guardrails/<skill>.md` |
| Feature intent and constraints | `feature-specs/<feature>/SPEC.md` |
| Workflow steps | `.ai/commands/<task>.md` |

## Workflow menu

When asked to perform one of these tasks, read the file first:

| Task | File |
|---|---|
| New feature | `.ai/commands/create-feature.md` |
| New repository | `.ai/commands/create-repository.md` |
| New service | `.ai/commands/create-service.md` |
| New route | `.ai/commands/add-route.md` |
| Debug a failure | `.ai/commands/debug.md` |
| Pre-ship review | `.ai/commands/review.md` |
| Refactor | `.ai/commands/refactor.md` |
| Feature progress | `.ai/commands/status.md` |
| Session checkpoint | `.ai/commands/checkpoint.md` |

Multi-step chains: `.ai/workflows/build-feature-end-to-end.md`,
`implement-feature.md`, `add-shopify-function.md`, `add-webhook.md`,
`add-ui-extension.md`, `migrate-schema.md`, `fix-bug.md`, `run-e2e.md`,
`rollback-feature.md`.

## Shopify surfaces

No `npx skill install` on this platform. For any task touching a Shopify API surface:

1. Map the surface via `.shopify/skills/registry.json`.
2. Read `.shopify/skills/guardrails/<skill>.md` — this is your primary Shopify context.
3. Verify any unknown field or mutation against `shopify.dev` before using it.
4. Flag anything unconfirmed as `UNVERIFIED: <field>` — do not ship it.
5. Every mutation must handle `userErrors`. Shopify GIDs only — no bare numeric IDs.

Surface → guardrail file map: `.shopify/skills/guardrails/README.md`.

## Validation

Run before declaring any task done:

```bash
npm run check
```
